Stalwarth Bond (2/day)	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Purple	Dragon Companion	VISIBLE:YES	KEY:Purple Dragon ~ Stalwarth Bond	DESC:Add half your Proficiency Bonus (round down) to any ability check or saving throw the dragon makes.													SORTKEY:PurpleDragonRaceTrait_2	SOURCEPAGE:UA